data.description: Have you been waiting for a turnkey home in the Las Posas Estates with magnificent views, open living and entertaining areas, and room to expand? This house has come to fulfill all your wishes and more! Nearly every room in the home has panoramic Topa Topa mountain and orchard views that bring in nature and stunning sunsets that make every day feel like vacation With over 2500 sqft of Trex view decks split on each level, many rooms have direct outdoor access allowing ample use of the amazing weather and views beyond. The home has had significant upgrades over the course of the current ownership, including new A/C and all new ductwork, as well as new paint and hardware throughout the home. On the lower level of the home is a large space that can easily be converted into an ADU with its own private staircase outside- allowing for the opportunity to have multifamily living or create income opportunities. This 4 bedroom/3 bathroom home has updated bathrooms and all of the rooms are well-proportioned with ample storage space. Other improvements include new furnace, retextured ceilings, owned solar, rose garden in the backyard, and an updated fireplace in the family room. The home is conveniently located and walkable to Las Posas Country Club- perfect for golf, tennis, and outdoor enthusiasts. Very few homes this turn-key come available in Las Posas Estates- don't miss out on the opportunity to make this yours!
